===Etymology===
{{zh-l|*於}} is a prefix to indicate respect for the dangerous animal; compare {{zh-l|老|old; venerable}} in {{zh-l|老虎|tiger}}.

{{zh-l|*菟}} is from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*k-la}}, from {{der|zh|mkh-pro|*klaʔ}}. Cognate with {{och-l|虎}}.
